{
  "info": {
    "name": "Fitness Coach API – Épico 1",
    "description": "Collection para testar Auth, Onboarding e Plans.\n\n**Ordem sugerida (sucesso):** 1) Signup, 2) Login, 3) PUT Profile, 4) PUT Goals, 5) POST Plans Weekly (201).\n**Cenário 422 Goals:** PUT Goals (expect 422).\n**Cenário 422 Plans:** Signup (user 422), Login (user 422), POST Weekly (expect 422).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "access_token_422", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Signup",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    console.log('Usuário criado. Agora use Login para obter o token.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"teste@email.com\",\n  \"password\": \"12345678\",\n  \"name\": \"Usuário Teste\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/signup",
            "description": "Cria usuário e perfil inicial. Respostas: 201 OK, 409 email já usado, 400 validação."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.access_token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', json.access_token);",
                  "        console.log('Token salvo na variável access_token.');",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"teste@email.com\",\n  \"password\": \"12345678\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "description": "Retorna JWT. O token é salvo automaticamente em access_token para as rotas de onboarding."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Forgot Password",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 - forgot password', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"teste@email.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/forgot-password",
            "description": "REQ-AUTH-003. Sempre 200. Se o e-mail existir, envia link por e-mail (em dev: stub loga no console). Rate limit 429. Para testar reset: obter token do último registro em password_reset_tokens (SELECT token FROM password_reset_tokens ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Reset Password",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 ou 400', function () {",
                  "    const code = pm.response.code;",
                  "    pm.expect([200, 400]).to.include(code);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"COLE_O_TOKEN_DO_EMAIL_OU_DO_BANCO\",\n  \"new_password\": \"novasenha123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/reset-password",
            "description": "REQ-AUTH-003. Token = valor recebido no link de e-mail (ou do banco após POST Forgot Password). new_password mínimo 8 caracteres. 200: sucesso; 400: token inválido/expirado."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Onboarding",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "PUT Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Usuário Teste\",\n  \"sex\": \"male\",\n  \"birth_date\": \"1990-01-15\",\n  \"weight_kg\": 80,\n  \"height_cm\": 175,\n  \"body_fat_percentage\": 22\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/onboarding/profile",
            "description": "Atualiza perfil biométrico. Requer JWT. Opcional: body_fat_visual_id (ex.: \"25\" ou \"medium\") em vez de body_fat_percentage."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT Goals",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"current_weight_kg\": 80,\n  \"current_body_fat_percent\": 22,\n  \"target_weight_kg\": 75,\n  \"target_body_fat_percent\": 18,\n  \"months_to_target\": 4,\n  \"intensity\": \"medium\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/onboarding/goals",
            "description": "Define meta de composição. Valida taxa de perda ≤ 1,5%/semana; se não passar retorna 422."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT Training Preferences",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"machines_only\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/onboarding/training-preferences",
            "description": "DD-ENT-TRAININGPREFERENCE. Define preferência de treino (apenas máquinas). Usado pelo POST /plans/weekly em summary.machines_only."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT Goals (expect 422)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 422 - meta fisiologicamente insegura', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(422);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Body contém mensagem sobre limite seguro', function () {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.message || body.error || '').to.include('1.5');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"current_weight_kg\": 80,\n  \"current_body_fat_percent\": 25,\n  \"target_weight_kg\": 60,\n  \"target_body_fat_percent\": 15,\n  \"months_to_target\": 2,\n  \"intensity\": \"high\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/onboarding/goals",
            "description": "Teste REQ-GOAL-001: meta com taxa de perda > 1,5%/semana (80→60 kg em 2 meses). Esperado: 422 e mensagem sobre limite seguro."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Plans",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Weekly",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 - plano semanal gerado', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Body contém weekly_plan_id e summary', function () {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('weekly_plan_id');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('start_date');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('end_date');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('target_kcal_per_day');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('summary');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.summary).to.have.property('daily_targets');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.summary).to.have.property('suggested_meals');",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Summary contém weekly_training e machines_only (SCN-TRAIN-ROTINA-MAQUINAS)', function () {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body.summary).to.have.property('weekly_training');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.summary.weekly_training).to.be.an('array');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.summary.weekly_training.length).to.equal(7);",
                  "    pm.expect(body.summary).to.have.property('machines_only');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.summary.machines_only).to.be.a('boolean');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/plans/weekly",
            "description": "Gera plano semanal (Motor de Metas: GCT Mifflin-St Jeor, déficit, TACO). Requer JWT e onboarding completo (profile + goals). 201: plano gerado; 422: dados de onboarding incompletos."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Signup (user 422)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"teste422@email.com\",\n  \"password\": \"12345678\",\n  \"name\": \"Usuário 422\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/signup",
            "description": "Cria segundo usuário para testar 422 em POST Plans Weekly (usuário sem profile/goals)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (user 422)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.access_token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token_422', json.access_token);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"teste422@email.com\",\n  \"password\": \"12345678\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "description": "Login do usuário que não tem profile/goals. Token salvo em access_token_422."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Weekly (expect 422)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 422 - onboarding incompleto', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(422);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Body contém mensagem sobre onboarding incompleto', function () {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    const msg = (body.message || '').toString();",
                  "    pm.expect(msg.toLowerCase()).to.match(/onboarding|perfil|metas/);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token_422}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/plans/weekly",
            "description": "Esperado 422: usuário com token de quem fez apenas Signup + Login (sem PUT profile nem PUT goals). Rodar após 'Signup (user 422)' e 'Login (user 422)'."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
